WEBVTT

00:00:00.580 --> 00:00:10.980
You know, I never thought donuts could make a morning feel this special, but sitting here at La Bonita Donuts, surrounded by all these fresh, colorful treats, it's impossible not to smile.

00:00:12.313 --> 00:00:18.233
The doughnuts are soft, fluffy, and you can really taste how fresh they are, like they were just made minutes ago!

00:00:19.160 --> 00:00:25.160
I love how there's something for everyone, from classic glaze to wild flavors I've never seen anywhere else.

00:00:27.357 --> 00:00:29.037
If you're looking for somewhere to start your day on a happy note, La Bonita Donuts is the spot!


